SKILL BASH

General Description:
  Bash is an attempt to knock your oppent down, by hitting him over the head.

Chance of Success:
  If your bash skill exceeds
    random(1,101) - dexterity modifier for you * 10
                  + dexterity modifier for oppenent * 10
                  + (something that should be changed)
  then you succeed.

Result of Success:
  Your victim takes 1 point of damage and is put into the sitting position.
  Your victim may not type commands for 2 rounds after being bashed.

Results of Failure:
  You do no damage, and fall down yourself.

Restrictions:
  You may not bash someone if more than 3 people are attacking you, or more
  than 5 people are attacking your victim.

  You may not type commands for 2 rounds regardless of the success or failure
  of this command.

  Bash may not be initiated in a peacful room.
